@startuml
' Deployment diagram
actor User
node "Browser / Mobile" as Client
node "Stays4Pilgrims Frontend Server / CDN" as CDN
node "Stays4Pilgrims Backend (NestJS)" as Backend
database "Postgres (managed)" as DB
Client -> CDN : GET static assets
CDN -> Backend : API calls
Backend -> DB : queries
note right of Backend : Env vars in .env (local development)
@enduml
